{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/aboutimage_1.png?t=1737554940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Mare is a unique fast-paced gripping survival horror game that mixes classic ghost story with a nerve-wracking survival horror experience. Prey that you will survive the evil forces that lurks in the shadows of this grand mansion. Move carefully, and hide when you can. Run as fast as you can, but for all the world don't get caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/TheMare_GIF4.gif?t=1737554940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a young boy trapped in an old mansion. In the game you can navigate through many of the rooms and corridors in the house, while trying to find clues and objects that are needed for the story to progress.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/img_features.png?t=1737554940\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/TheMare_GIF5.gif?t=1737554940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use stealth to avoid drawing attention from enemies. If necessary, hide under tables, beds or inside wardrobes. You can even use an old radio receiver that reveals the enemy's location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MAIN GAMEPLAY FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Walk, run, run, RUN! ...and maybe a little bit of crouching</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with doors and drawers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick up objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use stealth</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hide inside or under different kinds of furniture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Locate enemies and and see which 